ng tưởng - 望想</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/author-5S8czaSOqXhHlNE7NtKr8g">Đặng Trần Côn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-K%E1%BB%B3/Xu%C3%A2n-m%E1%BB%99-du-ti%E1%BB%83u-vi%C3%AAn/poem-WYT0lFJH2DPO2Ufdn0eSVw">Xuân mộ du tiểu viên - 春暮遊小園</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-K%E1%BB%B3/author-PptfiKstYrIhSNk8JxRO3w">Vương Kỳ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Quang-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-egf4hkr7y4OtzVnXgfU5nw">Xuân nhật hữu cảm kỳ 2 - 春日有感其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Quang-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-X3Oume1_mYQvTGcgMAhydQ">Trần Quang Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0ng-Th%E1%BA%BF-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-qu%E1%BB%91c-m%C3%B4n-t%C3%A1c/poem-mN9HaCRAVL597d38D-8Mlg">Xuất quốc môn tác - 出國門作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0ng-Th%E1%BA%BF-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-HJfO2lYVYcwt9Zclbkaj8A">Hàng Thế Tuấn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
